<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>FM FIRE SAFETY SOLUTION</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;600;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>
*{
margin:0;
padding:0;
box-sizing:border-box;
font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;
}

body{
background:#111;
color:white;
}

header{
background:linear-gradient(to right,#b30000,#ff3300);
padding:20px 10%;
display:flex;
justify-content:space-between;
align-items:center;
}

.logo{
font-size:22px;
font-weight:800;
color:white;
}

.logo span{
color:yellow;
}

nav a{
color:white;
text-decoration:none;
margin-left:20px;
font-weight:500;
}

.hero{
height:90vh;
display:flex;
align-items:center;
justify-content:center;
flex-direction:column;
text-align:center;
background:linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.7),rgba(0,0,0,0.7)),
url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1605902711622-cfb43c4437d1');
background-size:cover;
background-position:center;
}

.hero h1{
font-size:45px;
margin-bottom:20px;
}

.hero p{
font-size:18px;
margin-bottom:30px;
}

.btn{
background:#ff3300;
padding:12px 25px;
border:none;
color:white;
cursor:pointer;
font-weight:bold;
border-radius:5px;
}

section{
padding:80px 10%;
}

.section-title{
text-align:center;
font-size:32px;
margin-bottom:50px;
color:#ff3300;
}

.services{
display:grid;
grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(250px,1fr));
gap:30px;
}

.card{
background:#1c1c1c;
padding:30px;
border-radius:10px;
text-align:center;
transition:0.3s;
}

.card:hover{
transform:translateY(-10px);
background:#ff3300;
}

.why{
display:flex;
flex-wrap:wrap;
gap:30px;
justify-content:center;
}

.why div{
background:#1c1c1c;
padding:25px;
border-radius:10px;
width:250px;
text-align:center;
}

.contact{
background:#1c1c1c;
padding:50px;
border-radius:10px;
}

.contact input, .contact textarea{
width:100%;
padding:12px;
margin:10px 0;
border:none;
border-radius:5px;
}

footer{
background:#b30000;
text-align:center;
padding:15px;
margin-top:40px;
}

.whatsapp{
position:fixed;
bottom:20px;
right:20px;
background:#25D366;
color:white;
padding:15px;
border-radius:50%;
font-size:20px;
text-decoration:none;
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<header>
<div class="logo">🔥 <span>FM FIRE SAFETY SOLUTION</span></div>
<nav>
<a href="#">Home</a>
<a href="#services">Services</a>
<a href="#contact">Contact</a>
</nav>
</header>

<div class="hero">
<h1>Complete Fire Protection Services</h1>
<p>Installation | AMC | Fire Alarm | Hydrant | Sprinkler | Gas Suppression</p>
<button class="btn">Get Free Site Survey</button>
</div>

<section id="services">
<h2 class="section-title">Our Services</h2>
<div class="services">
<div class="card">
<h3>Fire Alarm System</h3>
<p>Complete fire alarm installation & maintenance.</p>
</div>
<div class="card">
<h3>Fire Extinguisher</h3>
<p>All types of fire extinguishers supply & refill.</p>
</div>
<div class="card">
<h3>Fire Hydrant System</h3>
<p>Industrial & commercial hydrant setup.</p>
</div>
<div class="card">
<h3>Sprinkler System</h3>
<p>Automatic fire sprinkler solutions.</p>
</div>
</div>
</section>

<section>
<h2 class="section-title">Why Choose Us?</h2>
<div class="why">
<div>Certified Company</div>
<div>Experienced Engineers</div>
<div>24x7 Support</div>
<div>Best Price Guarantee</div>
</div>
</section>

<section id="contact">
<h2 class="section-title">Contact Us</h2>
<div class="contact">
<input type="text" placeholder="Your Name">
<input type="email" placeholder="Your Email">
<textarea rows="5" placeholder="Your Message"></textarea>
<button class="btn">Send Message</button>
</div>
</section>

<a href="https://wa.me/919999999999" class="whatsapp">💬</a>

<footer>
© 2026 FM FIRE SAFETY SOLUTION | All Rights Reserved
</footer>

</body>
</html>
